{"id":913,"parent_id":909,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":913,"title":"Amos 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Amos","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord withholds rain, sends famine and pestilence, and destroys gardens and vineyards as judgments upon His people, yet they do not return unto the Lord."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.1","order":"02.31.004.61219"},["b","1"],"Hear this word, ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"kine"],"of Bashan, that",["i","are"],"in the mountain of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Samaria"],", which oppress the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"poor"],", which crush the needy, which say to their masters, Bring, and let us drink."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.2","order":"02.31.004.61220"},["b","2"],"The Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"hath sworn by his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"holiness"],", that, lo, the days shall come upon you, that he will take you away with hooks, and your posterity with fishhooks."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.3","order":"02.31.004.61221"},["b","3"],"And ye shall go out at the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"breaches"],", every",["i","cow at that which is"],"before her; and ye shall cast",["i","them"],"into the palace, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.4","order":"02.31.004.61222"},["b","4"],"¶Come to Beth-el, and transgress; at",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Gilgal"],"multiply transgression; and bring your sacrifices every morning,",["i","and"],"your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"tithes"],"after three",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"years"],":"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.5","order":"02.31.004.61223"},["b","5"],"And offer a sacrifice of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"thanksgiving"],"with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"leaven"],", and proclaim",["i","and"],"publish the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"free"],"offerings: for this liketh you, O ye children of Israel, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.6","order":"02.31.004.61224"},["b","6"],"¶And I also have given you",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"cleanness"],"of teeth in all your cities, and want of bread in all your places: yet have ye not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"returned"],"unto me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.7","order":"02.31.004.61225"},["b","7"],"And also I have withholden the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"rain"],"from you, when",["i","there were"],"yet three months to the harvest: and I caused it to rain upon one city, and caused it not to rain upon another city: one piece was rained upon, and the piece whereupon it rained not withered."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.8","order":"02.31.004.61226"},["b","8"],"So two",["i","or"],"three cities wandered unto one city, to drink water; but they were not satisfied: yet have ye not returned unto me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.9","order":"02.31.004.61227"},["b","9"],"I have smitten you with blasting and mildew: when your gardens and your vineyards and your fig trees and your olive trees increased, the palmerworm devoured",["i","them:"],"yet have ye not returned unto me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.10","order":"02.31.004.61228"},["b","10"],"I have sent among you the pestilence after the manner of Egypt: your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"young"],"men have I slain with the sword, and have taken away your horses; and I have made the stink of your camps to come up unto your nostrils: yet have ye not returned unto me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.11","order":"02.31.004.61229"},["b","11"],"I have overthrown",["i","some"],"of you, as God",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"overthrew"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"Sodom"],"and Gomorrah, and ye were as a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"firebrand"],"plucked out of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"burning"],": yet have ye not returned unto me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.12","order":"02.31.004.61230"},["b","12"],"Therefore thus will I do unto thee, O Israel:",["i","and"],"because I will do this unto thee, prepare to meet thy God, O Israel."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.13","order":"02.31.004.61231"},["b","13"],"For, lo, he that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"formeth"],"the mountains, and createth the wind, and declareth unto man what",["i","is"],"his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"thought"],", that maketh the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"morning"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"darkness"],", and treadeth upon the high places of the earth, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", The God of hosts,",["i","is"],"his name."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.1a","order":"02.31.004.61232"},["b","1a"],["span.small","IE"],"cows."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.1b","order":"02.31.004.61234"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/6.1"},"Amos 6:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.1c","order":"02.31.004.61236"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/20.2"},"2 Ne. 20:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.2a","order":"02.31.004.61238"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/89.35"},"Ps. 89:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.3a","order":"02.31.004.61240"},["b","3a"],["span.small","OR"],"broken places."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.4a","order":"02.31.004.61242"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.15.13-15"},"Hosea 9:15 (13–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.4b","order":"02.31.004.61244"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/14.28"},"Deut. 14:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/119.4.4-5"},"D&C 119:4 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.4c","order":"02.31.004.61246"},["b","4c"],["span.small","HEB"],"days."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.5a","order":"02.31.004.61248"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/thanksgiving"},"TG Thanksgiving"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.5b","order":"02.31.004.61250"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/leaven"},"TG Leaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.5c","order":"02.31.004.61252"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/22.18.18-21"},"Lev. 22:18 (18–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.6a","order":"02.31.004.61254"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/52.6"},"Jer. 52:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.6b","order":"02.31.004.61256"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hag/2.17"},"Hag. 2:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.3"},"Hel. 12:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.22.22-30"},"D&C 43:22 (22–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.7a","order":"02.31.004.61258"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/3.3"},"Jer. 3:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.10a","order":"02.31.004.61260"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.25"},"Isa. 3:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.33"},"D&C 45:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.11a","order":"02.31.004.61262"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.19"},"Isa. 13:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.11b","order":"02.31.004.61264"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/19.24"},"Gen. 19:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.11c","order":"02.31.004.61266"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/3.2"},"Zech. 3:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.11d","order":"02.31.004.61268"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1"},"Mal. 4:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/jude/1.23"},"Jude 1:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.13a","order":"02.31.004.61270"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-creator"},"TG Jesus Christ, Creator"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.13b","order":"02.31.004.61272"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/139.2"},"Ps. 139:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.5"},"Jacob 2:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/18.32"},"Alma 18:32"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.6"},"3 Ne. 28:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/33.1"},"D&C 33:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.13c","order":"02.31.004.61274"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.8"},"Amos 5:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"13d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.13d","order":"02.31.004.61276"},["b","13d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/8.9"},"Amos 8:9"],"."]]}
